name: The Sky Above Me (Yesterday)
description:
A companion to The Sky Above Me Every Hour (2021), a project where I display an image of where I am every hour, every day for a month. 

Instead of images, I describe what I was doing when yesterday's images were uploaded. I feel safer knowing that my memory of yesterday is now yours.

This NFT ends on November 30, 11:59pm, the day after it is minted.
